                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Email: <a className="contact-link" href="mailto:@gmail.com">nathan.yukio.stephens@gmail.com</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            LinkedIn: <a className="contact-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/i/" target="_blank">nathan-yukio-stephens</a> 
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            GitHub: <a className="contact-link" href="https://github.com/" target="_blank">nystephens</a> 
